    <keyword>TOPT-STAT</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This Telnet Option provides a way to determine the other Telnet module's view of the status of options.  This RFC specifies a standard for the ARPA Internet community.  Hosts on the ARPA Internet are expected to adopt and implement this standard.  Obsoletes RFC 651 (NIC 31154).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
